Result Report: Fraud Detection in Financial Transactions

Dataset: financial_transactions.csv on Github. This file has 10000 rows. 

Model Evaluation:
- **Accuracy:** 0.948

Classification Report:
```
              precision    recall  f1-score   support

           0       0.95      1.00      0.97      1896
